    <h3>Onions</h3>
    <p>
      Three onions for that day's cooking, maybe 400 to 500 grams. On Instamart, the smallest option is 1 kilogram at ₹28. The local vegetable vendor sells three onions for the price of three onions. She went to the vendor.
    </p>

