    <h3>Shampoo sachets</h3>
    <p>
      My mother uses one shampoo sachet per Sunday hair wash. At the kirana store, the entire back wall is covered in strips of Clinic Plus and Sunsilk sachets at ₹1 to ₹2 each. On Instamart, searching "shampoo sachet" returns bottles. The smallest unit is about ₹80. Two orders of magnitude difference, for the same product.
    </p>

