    <h3>Cashews</h3>
    <p>
      Instamart's smallest is 200 grams at ₹233. A household that wants to garnish a festival sweet with a few cashews does not need 200 grams. The kirana sells Classic Masala cashew strips at ₹10 per small packet.
    </p>

    <figure>
      <img src="/images/item-cashews.png" alt="Side by side comparison of cashews on Instamart (200g minimum at ₹233) and the kirana store's Classic Masala cashew strips at ₹10 per small packet" />
